metadata.name: First Day with billy
metadata.description:
A man and his dog, a bond so true,
Together through all life's adventures, they pursue.
Through fields of green, and paths of stone,
Their friendship, like a treasure, forever known.

In laughter and in tears, they share it all,
The man's best friend, always there to catch his fall.
Through thick and thin, in sun and rain,
Their love for one another, will forever remain.

With wagging tail and joyful bark,
The dog brings joy to the man's heart.
With loyalty and trust, so pure and true,
Their bond, a shining example for all to view.
